    "Basically, it is **f**.\n",
    "\n",
    "As we know, the derivative of **f(x)** with respect to **x** is\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\frac{df}{dx} = \\frac{f(x+h)-f(x)}{h}\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "So, for our function **L**,\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\frac{(d+h)\\cdot f - d\\cdot f}{h}\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "= \\frac{d\\cdot f + f\\cdot h - d\\cdot f}{h}\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "= \\frac{f\\cdot h}{h}\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "= \\mathbf{f}\n",
    "$$"
