    "Similarly, we calculated\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\frac{dL}{da}\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "which is\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\frac{dL}{da} = \\frac{dL}{de} \\cdot \\frac{de}{da}.\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "So,\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\frac{de}{da} = \\frac{d(a \\cdot b)}{da} = b.\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "Similarly,\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\frac{de}{db} = \\frac{d(a \\cdot b)}{db} = a.\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "Here we get our results:\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\mathbf{a.grad} = (-3.0) \\cdot \\frac{dL}{de} = 6.0\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\mathbf{b.grad} = (2.0) \\cdot \\frac{dL}{de} = -4.0\n",
    "$$"
   ]
